title: IAA Tonight | Giants DL Leonard Williams & Baker Mayfield Finally Gets Traded
description: Giants DL Leonard Williams joins Leger Douzable, Adam "Pacman" Jones and LeSean McCoy to discuss how things are going with his new head coach Brian Daboll, QB Daniel Jones, and the No. 5 overall pick in the 2022 NFL Draft Kayvon Thibodeaux. Will Daniel Jones have a breakout season for the Giants? Baker Mayfield was finally traded from the Cleveland Browns to the Carolina Panthers, but does he still have to fight for that starting spot?
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Leger Douzable, Adam "Pacman" Jones, LeSean McCoy, Leonard Williams)
